heading: Oblivion Dungeon Guide
content: Oblivion is a large dungeon that hosts the notorious exploding Fallen Lunatics, and has a convoluted layout that may require a great deal of backtracking. It is decent for farming, but is not currently a possible . There is no boss in this dungeon; once you destroy the 3 Fallen Idols at the end, the dungeon is complete. This dungeon unlocks the , a crowd control aspect usable by all classes. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! This dungeon is not accessible until you cleanse the evil in . This can be done solo, but goes by quicker with a group of friends. Reviewed by
